OL,3,CSix women make abuse claims against
OL,4,Cformer South Yorkshire officers
OL,6,FSix women have now come forward to
OL,7,Freport claims of child sex abuse as
OL,8,Fpart of an investigation into former
OL,9,Fpolice officers in South Yorkshire.
OL,11,FAn ex-constable, now in his fifties,
OL,12,Fwas arrested on Monday on suspicion of
OL,13,Fraping a teenage girl in Rotherham in
OL,14,F2004. He has since been released on
OL,15,Fbail.
OL,17,FIt follows the arrest of two former
OL,18,FSouth Yorkshire Police officers late
OL,19,Flast year on suspicion of sexual
OL,20,Foffences and misconduct in a public
OL,21,Foffice.
