OL,3,CSix women make abuse claims against
OL,4,Cformer South Yorkshire officers
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) is looking into
OL,8,Fcomplaints from survivors of child
OL,9,Fsexual exploitation and abuse in
OL,10,FRotherham.
OL,12,FIOPC director Emily Barry said: "We
OL,13,Fare now investigating serious
OL,14,Fcomplaints by six women of sexual
OL,15,Foffending by former South Yorkshire
OL,16,FPolice officers.
OL,18,F"These complaints are being handled
OL,19,Fsensitively and thoroughly
OL,20,Finvestigated and a third former
OL,21,Fofficer has now been arrested."
