OL,3,CSix women make abuse claims against
OL,4,Cformer South Yorkshire officers
OL,6,FThe offences are alleged to have taken
OL,7,Fplace while the officers, who were
OL,8,Fbased in Rotherham, were both on and
OL,9,Foff duty.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police referred itself
OL,12,Fto the IOPC in October 2024 after the
OL,13,Fincidents were first reported. This
OL,14,Fwas followed by more complaints from a
OL,15,Fsecond woman in November and two other
OL,16,Fwomen in December.
OL,18,FA fifth woman came forward in January,
OL,19,Ffollowed by the sixth last month.
